&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src= &#34;data:image/svg+xml;base64,&#34; data-lazy-src=&#34;https://www.helloimg.com/images/2022/02/27/GVE8AY.png&#34; alt=&#34;ygIOkb9ur1cdpMe&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
